Important caveats and exclusions

1. Vendor artifacts.
   Materials under `experiments/spider-farmer/original/` and
   `experiments/ecoflow-powerocean/original/` are vendored copies of
   third-party works (Android APKs, vendor PDFs, community-developed
   open-source integrations). They are NOT covered by this CC BY 4.0
   licence. Each carries its own copyright, and any redistribution must
   respect the original licence or vendor terms. Open redistribution
   caveats are listed in `docs/sources.md` and tracked in
   `docs/logbook.md`.

2. Recovered credentials and live operational data.
   Items flagged for redaction in `docs/sources.md` (notably entry
   S-SF-5) must NOT be redistributed even under CC BY 4.0. Redaction is
   a precondition for public release of derivatives.

3. AI-generated contributions and authorship.
   This work was prepared with substantial AI assistance from Claude
   (Anthropic; see `paper/references.bib` `anthropic2026claude` and
   the AI-disclosure section, paper/main.md § 9 / paper/main.tex
   sec:ai-disclosure). Under § 2 UrhG (German Copyright Act), copyright
   protection requires a "persönliche geistige Schöpfung" — a personal
   intellectual creation by a human. Outputs generated solely by an AI
   model do not, on the prevailing reading, qualify for independent
   copyright protection in Germany. The copyright in this work is
   therefore held by the human author named above, who has reviewed,
   curated, edited, and accepted every paragraph. The AI is acknowledged
   as a contributor in § 9.1, but is not and cannot be a co-author. See
   the footnote in paper/main.md § 9.1 / paper/main.tex sec:ai-disclosure
   for sources.

4. Statement of independence.
   This work is a hobbyist research project carried out by the author in
   a personal capacity. It is NOT part of, endorsed by, funded by,
   supervised by, or representative of the views of any employer,
   including the German Aerospace Center (DLR / Deutsches Zentrum für
   Luft- und Raumfahrt). See paper/main.md § 9.5
   ("Statement of independence and personal capacity").
